Package: options
Title: Improvements for R's global options/singleton functions.
Version: 0.3
Date: 2015-02-17
Authors@R: person("Christopher", "Brown", , "chris.brown@decisionpatterns.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides intuitive interface and seamless, lazy replacements for
    R's global option / singleton mechanism that encourages a cleaner (lazy)
    syntax and allows for deep retrieval and setting of options:
    e.g. get_option( foo$bar[['baz']] ) does what is expected.
url: URL: https://github.com/decisionpatterns/options
BugReports: https://github.com/decisionpatterns/options/issues
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
License: GPL-2
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
